verbose_text: These macrophages were of the Cx3cr1 + lineage and exhibited a pro inflammatory state more similar to classically activated than M2-type macrophages; however, their most distinguishing feature was the expression of solute carrier family 6 member 2 (Slc6a2; a known NE transporter), as well as monoamine oxidase A (MAOA), an enzyme that degrades NE.
